name: Sick Obsession
description:
Undo these chains, my friend, I'll show you the rage I've hidden. Perish the sacrament, swallow, but nothing's forgiven! You and I can't decide which of us was taken for granted, make amends, some of us are destined to be outlived. Step inside, see the Devil in I, too many times, we've let it come to this. Step inside, see the Devil in I, you'll realize I'm not your Devil anymore!

Oil, canvas, madness.
